{{1999 Conference USA football standings}}
The '''1999 Louisville Cardinals football team''' represented the [[University of Louisville]] in the [[1999 NCAA Division I-A football season|1999 college football season]]. The team, led by [[John L. Smith]], played their home games in [[Papa John's Cardinal Stadium]]. 

